data.description: NORTH CLEVELAND 5 BEDROOM HOME + POOL + SEPARATE LIVING QUARTERS - Welcome to the epitome of luxurious living in North Cleveland, where convenience meets elegance. Nestled in a prime city location, this remarkable 5-bedroom home offers endless space for everyone. From its spacious separate living quarters to the sparkling inground swimming pool, this property has it all! Dive into the beautiful inground swimming pool that's perfect for cooling off on hot summer days or hosting unforgettable poolside gatherings with the abundance of outdoor space. Relax on the ample patio and deck space, ideal for barbecues, sunbathing, or simply sipping your morning coffee. This property offers a unique feature - true separate living quarters with a separate entrance, two bedrooms, an office and carport. The kitchen is a chef's dream with an oversized layout, tons of cabinet and counter space, and elegant granite countertops. Whether you're preparing a family meal or hosting a dinner party, this kitchen has you covered. Altogether, 5 bedrooms and 3 updated bathrooms provide you with the comfort and privacy you crave. Located in the heart of the city, you'll be just a stone's throw away from the best restaurants, shops, and the scenic Greenway, ensuring you're always close to the action. This property is a rare gem that combines comfort, style, and convenience. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this one home!
